        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3470961234" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11598810877745127097">I was given this book to read by my father in law after he said it was one of his favorite books ever. It was okay, but honestly wasnt that great. Maybe because he hyped it up so much i was let down. It covers the life of Peitro a boy born on the same day as Emperor Frederick who was a real person. He had a bit of a crappy life with lots of hardships. There were some elements of romance and it was very much the traditional idea of historical fiction. Over all it was okay. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


