        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer239784115" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8663275077764789255">Overall, I liked this book. It was well researched and an entertaining story a la Sabatini/Shellebarger. My only real problem is that the author frequently put 20th Century attitudes into the mouth/thoughts of the protagonist.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


